history.content:
Hello All,

We have some availability for those seeking tutoring in the lower-division that I'd like to fill as soon as possible. It will be first come first served, and I appreciate your understanding that we won't be able to meet all demand. That being said, there should be a fair number of students who can get weekly tutoring for the remainder of the semester.

Go to CS370.org and create an account while indicating which course you are seeking help with. When a tutor selects your entry you'll be notified immediately.

Please feel free to email me any questions as I don't check Piazza very often.

Thank you!
history.subject: CS370 has some openings for those who are seeking tutoring in the lower-division! Sign up today!
